19) Q: Difference between Promise and Observable?

Answer:

Promise returns only one value.

Observable can return multiple values over time.

Observable supports operators like map, filter, debounceTime, retry, etc.

Observable is cancellable, Promise is not.

Angular mainly uses Observable for API handling.


